{"tid":1701183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3黑熊公路上搶救受傷小熊   女司機直擊心碎大喊「快救走孩子」","createTime":"2019-11-09T02:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T02:55:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4cb18902209a4c81004d3a79a04551790061cf","tid":1701183,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州一名女子蕾莎（Lesha Deshay）4日駕駛在伊莫卡利市（Immokalee）郊區，目睹三隻黑熊於車水馬龍的公路上拯救被車撞傷的小熊，黑熊家族無視危險幫助同伴的畫面讓蕾莎相當揪心。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，蕾莎4日晚間開車經過伊莫卡利市郊，看到三隻美洲黑熊在公路中央努力幫助後腿受傷的小熊，她趕緊將車停下並記錄整段過程，影片中可見受傷的小熊難以行走，三隻黑熊同伴不顧自身危險將其拉到路邊，揪心的景象讓蕾莎激動喊道，「天啊，有小熊被車撞了，快點救走你們的孩子吧！」<br />\n<br />\n當晚也有另一位女駕駛艾麗莎（Alisha Irons）目睹事件過程，並於事發後通報動保機構，據佛州魚類暨野生動物保育委員會（Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission）調查指出，受傷的小熊最後仍不幸死在遭撞地點附近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/11/08/phpQShWxP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F11%2F08%2FphpQShWxP.jpg&h=4a69d4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2972094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2972094&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=014fcd44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2972094&h=b5166ec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2972094</a>"},{"pid":"574caca7e08c08cb5de926971a11c9fc05ef283a","tid":1701183,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"早晨 <br />\n記得出門前 上 twitter retweet<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<br />\n（最新!!）Senator Rubio講議員被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=1ec2a60a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846%3Fs%3D19&h=370276c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846?s=19</a><br />\nSenator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=224ef15a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=421074cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&h=01c0cece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1031be3cf0bf785173efbbe7b72e7098960c7c43","tid":1701183,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b907f7365be3824d4ccf2